dc_description_s: These data layers represent public lands for Washburn County, Wisconsin in 2018. It is a feature class within the geodatabase, 'Washburn_PublicLands_2018.gdb'. The features included in this geodatabase are 'Washburn_County_Forest_2018', 'Washburn_DNR_Lands_2018', and 'Washburn_Federal_Lands_2018'.[County Forest: The County Lands layer for Washburn County is intended to represent County Lands referenced in the taxroll as described in legal descriptions and surveys. The polygons were extracted from the Tax Parcel polygons utilizing ownership information from the Tax Roll.Federal Lands: The Federal Lands layer for Washburn County is intended to represent Federal Lands referenced in the taxroll as described in legal descriptions and surveys. The polygons were extracted from the Tax Parcel polygons utilizing ownership information from the Tax Roll.]
uw_supplemental_s: This is an archived copy of the data held at UW-Madison. For the most current data available, please visit: https://www.co.washburn.wi.us/departments/land-info-surveyor-mapping/gis-data
